    "plan_content": "Here's a summary of the plan:\n\n## What will be created\n\n**4 new files** (no existing files modified):\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/ui/stepper.tsx` | Component implementation (new-york-v4 style) |\n| `apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/examples/stepper-demo.tsx` | Focused demo with 3-step controlled wizard |\n| `apps/v4/registry/bases/radix/ui/stepper.tsx` | Component implementation (radix base, Tailwind v4 selectors + `cn-` prefixes) |\n| `apps/v4/registry/bases/radix/examples/stepper-example.tsx` | Comprehensive example with 4 sub-scenarios (Basic, With Content, Vertical, Controlled) |\n\n**4 registry entries added** (one item appended to each `_registry.ts`):\n- `new-york-v4/ui/_registry.ts` — `stepper` UI entry\n- `new-york-v4/examples/_registry.ts` — `stepper-demo` example entry\n- `bases/radix/ui/_registry.ts` — `stepper` UI entry with `meta.links`\n- `bases/radix/examples/_registry.ts` — `stepper-example` entry with `title: \"Stepper\"`\n\nThe main `registry.ts` files in both namespaces **don't need modification** — they already spread `...ui` and `...examples` dynamically.\n\n## Component design highlights\n\n- **Two-level React context**: `StepperContext` (root: value, orientation) + `StepperItemContext` (per-item: step, isActive, isCompleted, defaulting to `null`)\n- **`StepperContent` dual-use**: inside a `StepperItem` (no prop needed, reads item context) OR standalone with explicit `step` prop (reads root context)\n- **Orientation-aware layout** via `data-orientation` + Tailwind group selectors — separators automatically switch between `h-px` (horizontal) and `w-px` (vertical)\n- **Controlled + uncontrolled**: `value`/`defaultValue`/`onValueChange` pattern matching Tabs\n- **`aria-current=\"step\"`** on active trigger; `role=\"presentation\"` on separator",
